      <title>壳牌气候呼吁促使荷兰集团推动更严格的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/shell-climate-appeal-sees-dutch-group-push-for-tougher-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家荷兰环保组织正在推动对 2021 年壳牌公司削减碳排放量的具有里程碑意义的法院命令进行更严格的解释，试图将该公司对该判决的上诉转化为对自己有利的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/shell-climate-appeal-sees-dutch-group-push-for-tougher-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>和特朗普一样，拜登也用政治捐款来支付律师费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/like-trump-biden-used-political-donations-to-cover-lawyer-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登曾批评共和党竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普依靠政治捐款来支付法律费用，他用民主党全国委员会筹集的近200万美元来支付自己的律师费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/like-trump-biden-used-political-donations-to-cover-lawyer-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开发商将在加拿大住宅建设中获得廉价土地租赁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/developers-to-get-cheap-land-leases-in-canadian-homebuilding-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府将向开发商提供公共土地的低成本租赁，并推动工厂化住宅建设，作为缓解加拿大住房危机的“历史性”计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/developers-to-get-cheap-land-leases-in-canadian-homebuilding-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西与中国关系加深，卢拉与亿万富翁 JBS 兄弟重聚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁巴蒂斯塔兄弟在被任命为 JBS SA 董事会成员后不到三周，就惊人地卷土重来，将他们推入巴西最高权力圈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/lula-reunites-with-billionaire-jbs-brothers-as-brazil-s-china-ties-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:54:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和西班牙在直布罗陀协议方面取得“重大进展”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-spain-make-significant-progress-toward-gibraltar-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和西班牙表示，在英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦、西班牙外交大臣和直布罗陀首席部长周五举行会谈后，英国和西班牙在解决脱欧后直布罗陀边境安排的协议方面取得了“重大进展”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/uk-spain-make-significant-progress-toward-gibraltar-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰承诺 2024 年额外提供 14 亿欧元支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/war-in-ukraine-dutch-commit-an-extra-1-4-billion-in-2024-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰今年承诺额外提供 14 亿欧元（15 亿美元）支持乌克兰，因为这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家请求提供更多援助以击退俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/war-in-ukraine-dutch-commit-an-extra-1-4-billion-in-2024-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
